            <h2>Who are we</h2>
            <p>Colour Up is an independent social climbing group that focuses on bringing individuals from ethnic minorities together. The group is for those aged 16+. They offer informal and inclusive sessions, run by fellow climbers members just like you. No experience is necessary to attend. There will be a Colour Up representative at each session to help introduce you to other like-minded individuals.</p>
