                <h2>Where we meet</h2>
                <p>We are blessed with so many great climbing gyms here in Bristol (our home) that we like to meet at alternate ones each week. 
                    They include, Redpoint, Flashpoint & TCA. Anddd when the weather is kind to us, we like to grab our gear and head outdoors.
                </p>
